Package eu.focusnet.app.ui.fragment

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BookmarkFragment
    This fragment is inserted in the ProjectsListingActivity when the user clicks the "Bookmarks" entry in the Drawer menu.
    FragmentManager
    Helper class for handling Fragments
    PageFragment
    This fragment will be loaded from the PageActivity and displays a dashboard consisting of widgets.
    ProjectFragment
    This fragment will be loaded from ProjectActivity or ProjectInProjectActivity and displays the different dashboards, tools and inner projects of ProjectInstance.
    ProjectsListingFragment
    This fragment is the start point of the application after the user logged in.
